  m_text: "<align=center>HOW TO PLAY\n\nMOVEMENT\nA / D \u2014 Move\nSpace \u2014
    Jump\nQ \u2014 Rotate gravity left\nE \u2014 Rotate gravity right\n\nOBJECTIVE\nReach
    the exit portal at the end of each chamber\n\nCOLLECTIBLES\nFind the hidden star
    in each chamber\n\nTIPS\nRotating gravity changes which surface you fall toward\nYou
    can walk on walls and ceilings after rotating\nAvoid the red spikes\n\nPress
    ESC or click Back to return"
